HEADWORD: Clearcole
<hw>Clear"cole`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>claire
colle</ets> clear glue; <ets>clair</ets> clear (f. <ets>claire</ets>) +
<ets>colle</ets> glue, Gr. <?/.]</ety> <def>A priming of size mixed with
whiting or white lead, used in house painting, etc.; also, a size upon
which gold leaf is applied in gilding.</def>⟦br⟧
